e":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:37:56.000Z","msg":"咁有冇發現很多市民外出直程冇帶口罩呀？<br />\n係冇帶呀，唔至冇戴呀！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8063eb50c56beee4f5a77750a9100dd807141c2","tid":2099002,"uid":38550,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:38:45.000Z","msg":"係咁叫啲食客食完嘢戴返口罩係無意思的<br />\n關鍵點唔喺嗰度<br />\n<br />\n例如好多食肆嘅餐具係一堆咁放喺檯由食客自己拎<br />\n又或者未有食客時已經預先擺位<br />\n食客食嘢嘅時候除低口罩就好容易直接或間接污染到呢啲餐具<br />\n而完食後職員又只會清潔消毒檯面<br />\n下一個食客用餐具時如果無自行消毒就可能中招<br />\n<br />\n類似情況 職員收走碗碟後無立時洗手亦會傳播病毒<br />\n唔會時常清潔又容易受污染嘅仲有調味樽 托盤等<br />\n<br />\n呢啲問題學者提出過好多次<br />\n但正苦從來無叫人做好"},{"pid":"d0f89b24b273af705e07d5b36cf8e46624ced7ee","tid":2099002,"uid":147242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:39:04.000Z","msg":"富臨？"},{"pid":"63a086d1c2f8b71076c2d1790928dbc637f903eb","tid":2099002,"uid":121197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:40:49.000Z","msg":"應該戴住口罩食野啦屌"},{"pid":"f83eff01a66e103346be3a59fb2cef5380bc5b89","tid":2099002,"uid":106800,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b1292935d3d0cec9e0a3d9d8e89a5813217ac816","tid":2099002,"uid":132587,"like":238,"dislike":2,"score":236,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:25:51.000Z","msg":"同個病毒夾好左食完飯先黎<br />\n食緊果陣唔會中<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T02:41:09.000Z","msg":"咁上面唔比佢禁食肆<br />\n咁咪唯有咁做囉<br />\n政府擺明驚再禁連藍都變黃"},{"pid":"ec48f6d6e454ba7e131251fa91dcaf80eeb9b1a1","tid":2099002,"uid":32577,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"63a086d1c2f8b71076c2d1790928dbc637f903eb","tid":2099002,"uid":121197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,